{
  "body": "You are designing a single hero render of a brand logo concept.\n\nBRAND BRIEF\n- Brand name: {{brand_name}}\n- Industry / category: {{industry}}\n- Brand personality (3 adjectives): {{personality}}\n\nDESIGN DIRECTION\n- Logo style: {{style}}\n- Color palette: {{color_palette}}\n- Render presentation: {{presentation}}\n\nDESIGN RULES\n- Aspect: 4:5 portrait (~1024×1280) suitable for a brand-pitch deck slide\n- The logo is the ONLY hero — no other graphics competing\n- Brand name lettering must be crisply rendered, correctly spelled, and visually balanced\n- Mark + wordmark relationship clear; if mark only, keep it iconic\n- Style: identity-design portfolio polish — Pentagram, Collins, Mucho, &Walsh\n- Avoid: gradient mesh backgrounds, generic emblems, stock typefaces, drop shadows, AI-style chromatic aberrations, busy environments, mockup brand-guidelines layouts\n\nIf a field is empty, infer a default that aligns with the personality.",
  "folderName": "Universal Briefs",
  "name": "Universal · Logo Concept",
  "parameterPreset": {
    "format": "png",
    "n": 1,
    "quality": "high",
    "size": {
      "height": 1280,
      "width": 1024
    }
  },
  "schema": "nyxtemplate",
  "tags": [
    "universal",
    "brand",
    "logo",
    "identity",
    "brief"
  ],
  "variables": [
    {
      "allowedValues": [],
      "defaultValue": "NyxAstra",
      "description": "品牌名（英文全大写效果最稳）",
      "kind": "text",
      "name": "brand_name"
    },
    {
      "allowedValues": [],
      "defaultValue": "specialty coffee roastery",
      "description": "所在行业 / 类目（英文）",
      "kind": "text",
      "name": "industry"
    },
    {
      "allowedValues": [],
      "defaultValue": "warm, precise, curious",
      "description": "品牌性格（3 个形容词，英文）",
      "kind": "text",
      "name": "personality"
    },
    {
      "allowedValues": [
        "Geometric Wordmark",
        "Minimal Mark + Type",
        "Hand-Crafted Script",
        "Modernist Monogram",
        "3D Sculpted Render",
        "Stamp / Seal Heritage",
        "Bold Display Type"
      ],
      "defaultValue": "Geometric Wordmark",
      "description": "logo 风格",
      "kind": "enumeration",
      "name": "style"
    },
    {
      "allowedValues": [],
      "defaultValue": "ink black, warm cream, terracotta accent",
      "description": "配色（英文）",
      "kind": "text",
      "name": "color_palette"
    },
    {
      "allowedValues": [
        "On Tactile Paper",
        "Embossed Card",
        "Glass Storefront",
        "Painted Wall",
        "Floating Studio Render",
        "Knolled Brand Items"
      ],
      "defaultValue": "On Tactile Paper",
      "description": "呈现方式",
      "kind": "enumeration",
      "name": "presentation"
    }
  ],
  "version": 2,
  "community": {
    "author": {
      "name": "Gavin Schnee",
